Author: joseph_anderson_
Content:
Hey @everyone even though there's no stream today I wanted to do a quick announcement about an upcoming stream feature I'm super excited about. 13 Sentinels will continue on main days next week of course, and Fridays-on-Saturdays will resume as their own playthrough of some smaller games that people want to see, but we're going to be adding ONE MORE THING in the form of an UMINEKO READTHROUGH.

It's been long requested and in high demand from the weebs that control everything about this platform, so I've decided to give in. This is not an April Fool's joke. I really mean it. We will be starting the Umineko feature.

So without further delay I am incredibly thrilled to announce UMINEKO WEDNESDAYS ON A LEAPDAY. Look out for it. ğŸ‘

Content:

Streams will still happen this week. RE4 Remake -> New Jedi game. But saturday streams will probably be on hold for a while. RIP Atomic Heart. I am such a good streamer. Good thing we finished Forspoken in time. PHEW.

After these two games I'll likely take another week stream break to finish the rest of the this, while doing what I can with the workflow I have set up between the streams we do. Then we'll continue on as normal with all of this behind us.
